channel.title: Skillzlyfe Reborn
channel.description:
I have been working on many projects that I decided to quit because there was just too much work to be done. Many people may hate me for using Delta as a base but I have Grahams event manager and I have also cleaned out the process a bit.
Here is the link of what Skillzlyfe used to look like before I released it.[url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,468597.msg3425841.html#msg3425841]CLICK HERE[/url]
The reason for me remaking this is because I noticed that quite a few people love old school servers and this was a fun old school based server I created roughly 4-5 years ago. I hit a maximum of 80+ people online at once with no lagg.
To check out all the updates of the server please visit [url=http://skillzlyfe.comxa.com/]http://skillzlyfe.comxa.com/[/url]
Here is a little video of thieving. [url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dJ369rOnzXU]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dJ369rOnzXU[/url]
You may see thieving as crappy with a rubbish event but this is soon all to be changed.
Pictures shall be coming soon as I have cleaned out npc drops, shops, autospawn, npchandler, wanneshop in the client class and much more.
